{
  "stem": "3103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And any child can be thrilled with this, so I guess I was also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was David.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He still is alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He is in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Comes from a very fine family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a few years older, so when I finished school, he was already in Sosnowiec in high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't see him since-- I didn't see him during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after the war when the first time we went to Israel in 1964, I met quite a few survivors, and he was one of them also.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he was married at the time, which I was delighted, and he was the only survivor from his family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His sister was a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's why I befriended myself with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would explain that the boyfriend is not to that extreme the way it's in the United States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You used to go to school, maybe you went out skating once with him, but it wasn't hanging out to a movie go or hanging out for ice cream.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just at-- in the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It made you feel he's there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I cannot express my feelings now as was a young kid how you felt towards-- but they knew he was my boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea because I was very young and we never went in talking to each other, I love you, I miss you, whatever, never happened.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, just a school friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At my own hometown, I wasn't aware of anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But where my grandparents lived in Sosnowiec, there used to be a main street called [POLISH]-- this street in Polish.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
